net.openhft.chronicle.algo.bitset

Interface BitSetFrame.Bits

  • Enclosing interface:
    BitSetFrame

    public static interface BitSetFrame.Bits
    An iteration of bits in a bit set.

    Usage idiom: 

    
 Bits bits = bitSet.setBits();
 for (long bit; (bit = bits.next()) >= 0;) {
     // do something with the bit
 }
